This ability opens a celestial gate and calls forth an angelic deva to fight at the caster's side until the ability expires or the deva's earthly avatar is slain.

Characteristics of a deva:
 - Hit Points: 110
 - Armor Class: -11
 - 70% resistance to magic
 - 100% resistance to cold, fire, and electricity
 - 10% resistance to crushing, slashing, piercing, and missile damage
 - Immune to backstab
 - Immune to non-magical weapons and enchanted weapons +1
 - Immune to charm, confusion, feeblemind, level drain, petrification, poison, and slay
