 - Combat: 2 attack per round at -3 THAC0 for 3d6 +14 crushing damage; Dispel Magic on target each hit; undead take an extra 1d6 +2 crushing damage and must save vs. death at -4 or be utterly destroyed; strikes as an enchanted weapon +3~
@10060 = ~Berserk

Duration: 2 turns
Area of Effect: The caster

The character goes berserk 2 turns. He gains a +2 bonus to Strength and Dexterity, and becomes immune to charm, confusion, fear, feeblemind, hold, imprisonment, level drain, maze, stun, and sleep; he also gains 15 temporary Hit Points. When the state ends, the character will take 15 points of piercing damage.~
@10061 = ~Invoke Courage

Duration: 5 turns
Casting Time: 2
Area of Effect: The caster

When Mazzy uses this ability, she becomes immune to fear and gains a +1 bonus to THAC0 as well as to all Saving Throws. The effect lasts for 5 turns.~
@10062 = ~Lay On Hands

Duration: Permanent
Casting Time: 1
Area of Effect: The caster

Mazzy channels positive energy to heal herself for 2 Hit Points per level.~
@10063 = ~Haste

Duration: 3 rounds +1 round/level
Casting Time: 3
Area of Effect: The caster

When circumstances demand it, Mazzy can move at incredible speeds for brief periods of time. Using this ability, she resembles nothing so much as a body imbued with a wizard's Haste spell; she can run twice her normal distance in the same amount of time, receives an additional attack in each round of combat, and gains a -2 initiative bonus. Such a pace cannot be maintained indefinitely, however. The effect only lasts for 3 rounds +1 round per level before she slows again to her standard speed.~
@10064 = ~Strength

Duration: Special
Casting Time: 2
Area of Effect: The caster

When necessary, Mazzy can draw upon a great well of strength for brief periods of time. Using this ability sets her Strength to 18/50 for 3 turns. Upon reaching level 7, the Strength sets to 18/75 for 3 turns. Upon reaching level 13, the Strength increase is to 18/00, and she receives an additional +4 THAC0 bonus to all attacks for 39 rounds. Such might cannot be sustained indefinitely, alas. When the ability ends, the power coursing through her body ebbs, and Mazzy's Strength returns to normal levels.~
@10065 = ~Create Bruiser Mates

Duration: Permanent
Casting Time: 9
Area of Effect: The caster

This ability crafts five of Jan's patented Flasher Master Bruiser Mates, adding them to the character's inventory. Handle with care!~
@10066 = ~Cure Light Wounds

Range: Touch
Duration: Permanent
Casting Time: 1
Area of Effect: 1 creature

By casting this ability and laying his hand upon a creature, the caster causes 8 points of wound or other injury damage to the creature's body to be healed. This healing cannot affect creatures without corporeal bodies, nor can it cure wounds of creatures not living or of extraplanar origin. Curing is permanent only insofar as the creature does not sustain further damage; caused wounds will heal, or can be cured, just as any normal injury.~
@10067 = ~Slow Poison

Range: Touch
Duration: Instant
Casting Time: 1
Area of Effect: 1 creature

When this ability is placed upon a poisoned individual, it greatly slows the effects of venom, actually neutralizing all but the most deadly poisons.~
@10068 = ~Draw Upon Holy Might

Duration: 1 turn
Casting Time: 10
